EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[11]</span></span><![endif]></span></span></span></a><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>I have discussed we-intentions as shared
we-attitudes in the 1980’s and later more generally as applicable to all kinds
of attitudes (see e.g. Tuomela and Miller, 1988, Tuomela, 1995, Tuomela and
Bonnevier-Tuomela, 1997, Balzer and Tuomela, 1997, Tuomela, 2002, Tuomela, 2005b).<o:p></o:p></span></p>

</div>

