lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%'><span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>  </span>In other contexts (e.g. Tuomela, 2002,
Tuomela and Tuomela, 2003) I have characterized the we-mode in terms of three
features: (1) the attitude or action must be collectively accepted as the
