EN-US;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA'>[22]</span></span><![endif]></span></span></span></a><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;line-height:150%'> The discussion in Tuomela
(2002), Chapters 3 and 4, of collective pattern-governed behavior, generalizing
